title: Shocking cause of death of tot girl, Mariah Woods
itunes:title: Shocking cause of death of tot girl, Mariah Woods
description:
The autopsy of little Mariah Woods reveals the North Carolina girl died from chloroform poisoning, leading to murder charges against her mother's live-in boyfriend. Nancy Grace explores the newest evidence in the case with forensics expert Joseph Scott Morgan, New York psychologist Caryn Stark, and Jacksonville Daily News Mike McHugh,
